# Volatile API cache stays out of git, but two things are irreplaceable and must be kept:
# - data/cache/archive/  : the full 2025-26 season harvested before the FPL July wipe
# - perfect_season_*.json: MILP scenario results computed on that frozen season
data/cache/*
!data/cache/archive/
!data/cache/archive/**
!data/cache/perfect_season_*.json
